Search the Web
==============

A simple Yahoo BOSS v2 search application using django and oauth


Usage notes
-----------

To sort by a ranking other than Yahoo, place a sort switch in
your query, eg 'Jensen Button sort:alexa'


Dependencies
------------

Python 2.6+
Django 1.1+
django-oauth-consumer

if serving with Apache:
    apache2.2
    mod-wsgi 

VirtualHost config (Apache)
---------------------------

# Security notes:
#
# 1. Because django.wsgi is inside a folder containing other
#    code, make it available specifically, rather than by
#    unlocking it's parent directory.
#
# 2. Static content is best served by Apache, rather than
#    django.

<VirtualHost *:80>

    ServerName yourservername.com
    ServerAlias www.yourservername.com

    Alias /static/ /path/to/django-snippets/static/
    <Directory /path/to/django-snippets/static/>
        AllowOverride None
        Options all 
        Order deny,allow
        Allow from all 
    </Directory>

    WSGIScriptAlias / /path/to/django-snippets/django.wsgi
    <Files /path/to/django-snippets/django.wsgi>
        Order deny,allow
        Allow from all 
    </Files>

</VirtualHost>
